snippet.title: Rag Doll Kung Fu™ Trailer
snippet.description:
All the puppets were kung fu fighting!  Developed by Tarsier Studios, Rag Doll Kung Fu™: Fists of Plastic is a PS3™ exclusive party-fighting game that delivers a sharp jab to the funny bone with the craziest cast of fighters in the history of kung fu.  The completely customizable puppet characters bend, stretch, and snap to perform every move with hilarious results.  Watch this trailer today for a preview of this April 9th release.

http://www.us.playstation.com/PS3/Games/Rag_Doll_Kung_Fu_Fists_of_Plastic

Rag Doll Kung Fu™ Fists of Plastic ©2008 Sony Computer Entertainment Europe. Developed by Tarsier Studios AB. Rag Doll Kung Fu is a trademark of Mark Healey.
